DSIT COMMUNITY LICENSE v0.1 (Draft)

This is a lightweight license draft intended to express:
- free use for law enforcement and non-commercial research/education
- commercial use requires a separate commercial license with IP participation up to 5%

IMPORTANT: This text is not legal advice. Organizations should obtain legal review before adoption.

PERMISSIONS (NON-COMMERCIAL / LE)
You may use, modify, and redistribute DSIT for:
- law enforcement / justice-system functions
- non-commercial academic research
- non-commercial educational use

RESTRICTIONS (COMMERCIAL)
Commercial use (directly or indirectly monetized DSIT-enabled services) requires a separate commercial agreement.

ATTRIBUTION
Retain this license notice in source distributions.

NO WARRANTY
Provided “AS IS”, without warranty of any kind.

CONTACT
Commercial licensing / participation: see docs/IP_PARTICIPATION_ADDENDUM.md
